                    <span>Excellently done except: there are no captions, and the dialog is drowned out with musical instruments, making parts next to impossible for those with impared hearing to understand. What a pity.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Buy the original BBC edition, not this A&E version</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
